message.body: Yo! How did things go with Annie?
She emailed me back and said she wanted to back about it, but hasn't called me back yet
Did you receive the email I cc-d you on with her?

Oh good okay. Hope it's a good phone call...ugh this waiting is annoying! And Yes I did! Just saw it yesterday. I will follow up and say hi again too. My trip was good! My friend and I did some guerrilla street art lol, it was fun.
This weekend will be the first weekend I'm around in three weeks lol so weird
